query:
SELECT s.companyName, sr.serviceType, sr.serviceLevel, sr.rateUsdCents, sr.countryCode, sr.cityId
FROM suppliers s 
JOIN supplierRates sr ON s.id = sr.supplierId 
WHERE sr.countryCode = 'AU' 
  AND sr.serviceType = 'L1_NETWORK' 
  AND sr.serviceLevel = 'next_business_day'
  AND sr.cityId IS NULL
ORDER BY s.companyName;
